high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
Turn left and step forward to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave, heat it, and then pick the cup back up.
Turn around, take a step and turn left to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To heat a cup and put it back in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the microwave on the left.
Heat the mug in the coffee machine.
Bring the heated mug back to the coffee machine.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave.
Place the cup in the microwave, heat it up, and take it out of the microwave.
Turn around and head back towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the cup on the coffee maker.
